message: To succeed, prioritize combining one magical and one mundane liquid ingredient, then apply the 'filter' tool for high scores. message: To reach 100 points, combine 'ghostly vapor' (magical gas) with 'tree sap' (mundane liquid). Then, use the 'filter' tool on the resulting item. This combination yields two 'filtered' liquid components, giving 100. Other mundane liquids created with the 'vial' tool (like 'frog leg extract' or 'rose petal extract') combined with a magical gas will give 80 after filtering, due to one 'poorly-filtered' component. Avoid combining gases with solid ingredients directly before filtering, as this often leads to lower scores with 'botched filtering' on the solid.
